# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Navigator CRM — public-source provider keys
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# All keys are OPTIONAL. Without them, the app still runs — it just
# uses the zero-key providers (Clearbit, Gravatar, unauthed GitHub,
# SEC EDGAR, Wikidata, GLEIF, ORCID).
#
# Adding any of these free keys unlocks more sources / higher rate
# limits.  See docs/DATA-SOURCES.md for full details.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the keys you want to
# enable. `.env.local` is gitignored.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# GitHub Personal Access Token (free)
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scope needed: public_repo (or just no scopes — raising rate limit works with no scopes)
# Without key: 60 req/hr.  With key: 5000 req/hr.
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# OpenCorporates developer token (free, 500 req/month)
# Sign up at: https://api.opencorporates.com
# Unlocks: 200M+ global companies across 140+ jurisdictions
OPENCORPORATES_TOKEN=

# UK Companies House API key (free, unmetered)
# Sign up at: https://developer.company-information.service.gov.uk
# Unlocks: Entire UK corporate registry
COMPANIES_HOUSE_TOKEN=

# SAM.gov Entity API key (free, 1000 req/day)
# Sign up at: https://sam.gov/content/api
# Unlocks: US federal contractor registry (UEI lookups, post-DUNS)
SAM_GOV_TOKEN=

# Hunter.io API key (free tier: 25 searches/month)
# Sign up at: https://hunter.io
# Unlocks: Domain → named-contact email discovery (key contacts on enrichment)
HUNTER_TOKEN=
